<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2011-03-16</DATELINE><TITLE>Myocarditis Caused by Human Parainfluenza Virus in an Immunocompetent Child Initially Associated with 2009 Influenza A (H1N1) Virus</TITLE><BODY>The association between respiratory viruses and myocarditis has hardly ever been described. We report a case of acute myocarditis in an immunocompetent child associated with the presence of parainfluenza virus type 3 infection, in a context of recent influenza illness, confirmed by molecular and serological studies.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>